ón de las técnicas de Manejo integrado de Cultivos (MIC)\" font_container=\"tag:p|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"pt-xs\" width=\"1/12\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-1 vc_col-md-1 vc_col-xs-4\"][vc_single_image image=\"713\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"pt-xs\" width=\"5/12\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-5 vc_col-md-5 vc_col-xs-8\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Sociales\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"pb-xs\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Disminuye la cantidad de accidentes de trabajo<br />\r\nOtorga capacitaciones a los trabajadores y aumenta el sentido de pertenencia<br />\r\nMejora las relaciones con la comunidad<br />\r\nMejora la imagen corporativa y la reputación\" font_container=\"tag:p|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"py-xxs\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Proceso de certificación\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"extra-bold pb-sm\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-6 vc_col-xs-12\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Técnico\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%2383836c\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"pb-md\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"DIAGNÓSTICO\" font_container=\"tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23578820\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"font-bold pb-md\" css=\".vc_custom_1556561982137{background-image: url(http://responsiblesoy.loc/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/chevron-diagnostico.png?id=730) !important;background-position: right 5px !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"A cargo del Técnico<br />\r\nFacilitador\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%23578820\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"pb-md\"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-l